<h2 class="text-center">Arra të Mbushura me Fik (Walnut Stuffed Syrupy Figs)</h2>
<div class="smaller-space"></div>
<div class="container-fluid well well-lg">
    <div class="row">
        <div class="col-md-12">
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-md-4">
                    <br /><br />
                    <img class="img-responsive" src="~/Images/Albania/Starters/Figs_and_Walnuts.webp" alt="Figs and Walnuts" />
                    <br />
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-4">
                    <br />
                    <div class="text-left"><h2>Ingredients</h2></div>
                    <br/><br />
                    <ul>
                        <li>4 Fresh Figs</li>
                        <li>8 Walnut Halves</li>
                        <li>150ml Water</li>
                        <li>60g Sugar</li>
                    </ul>
                    <br /><br />
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-4">
                    <h2 class="text-center">Method</h2>
                    <br />
                    <ol class="text-justify">
                        <li>
                            Cut off the hard bits of stalk and then cut the figs in half length ways.
                            <br /><br />
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            Place the figs in a frying pan with the cut side face up and add the water around them. Leave the figs on a medium heat to cook through, once they become soft remove them from the pan and place onto a serving dish (this will take around 10 - 15 minutes).
                            <br /><br />
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            In the pan there will be a red water juice left from the figs. Add the sugar while remaining on a medium heat. Stir continuously for a couple of minutes until the juice has turned to a thick syrup. Remove from the heat.
                            <br /><br />
                        </li>
                        <li>Push one half of walnut into every fig and then drizzle the syrup over the top. Serve warm or cooled.</li>
                    </ol>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

